sql:
SELECT SUM(total_energy) AS total_energy_consumed
FROM energy_consumption_summary
WHERE time_period = 'weekly';

external_knowledge:
- 1593420000 and 1593420000 + 86400 represent a 24-hour period starting from June 30, 2020, 00:00:00 UTC; 
- 'good' data quality implies reliable data; 
- The time range covers a single day.

- High energy usage nodes refer to those with an average energy consumption greater than 500; 
- Main node refers to the node with a root node ID of 1.
- July 2021 represents the time period between timestamps 1625097600 and 1627776000.

